    evolutionary: "The soul brought the awakening impulse into the deepest sphere of transformation — suggesting a pre-birth intention to break through to what lies below the most defended layers of self. The configuration implies that the soul chose an incarnation in which the normal defenses against radical change would not hold — where the very mechanisms of protection would become sites of liberation. The pre-birth intention appears to involve demonstrating that what survives the most thorough dissolution is not what was defended, but what was always already real. The chart indicates a soul that elected the most difficult possible curriculum as the fastest path to a particular kind of knowing.",
