    evolutionary: "The soul that chose this configuration carries a pre-birth intention to discover that love of the particular and love of the universal are not competing claims but a single motion at different scales. The Venus-sphere here suggests a soul who arrives with the feeling life already oriented outward toward humanity, carrying the intention to work out in close personal bonds what it understands theoretically about connection and community. The cosmological task is to allow the warmth that extends easily to the many to also settle, without loss of freedom, into the intimacy of the one — to discover that genuine closeness does not require the surrender of one's larger orientation.",
